                                                    <span class="hoverShadow"></span><a href="{{ asset('images/produits/'~produit.id~'_'~produit.parent.id~'.png') }}" title="Summer Childcare Questions" rel="prettyPhoto[slideshow]" class="inited"><span class="hoverIcon"></span></a></div>
                                                <h4>
